I think if we were look at either India in
either the dimension of

00:00:20.531 --> 00:00:25.030
talent, in the dimension of power, it could
be many things to many

00:00:25.030 --> 00:00:26.980
people.
To me, I think fundamentally, we are a very

00:00:26.980 --> 00:00:31.080
tolerant country.
So intrinsically, we have the ability to do

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:34.930
what people wanted to do,
so I think tolerance, the underlying essence

00:00:34.930 --> 00:00:38.230
of what we do and our
focus has been built around that.

