00:01:00.539 --> 00:01:03.859
I think super is an objective, again, is a
superlative in terms of what

00:01:03.859 --> 00:01:07.230
we could do as a nation.
If you were to intrinsically leverage some

00:01:07.230 --> 00:01:11.990
