I think what people are been typically have
been doing is an inward,

00:01:36.650 --> 00:01:40.630
awkward look in terms of saying, hey, this
is the India is the outside

00:01:40.630 --> 00:01:43.350
environment, and it's time for the others
to look at us in terms of

00:01:43.350 --> 00:01:46.870
