extreme capability in terms of what we could

00:02:19.660 --> 00:02:24.090
do in this space to be
able to achieve what we would typically call

00:02:24.090 --> 00:02:26.360
a superpower.
So I think it's in us.

00:02:26.360 --> 00:02:29.640
It's each one of us in terms of our ability
to believe in oneself and

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:34.810
say hey I think we are, you know, a nation
